        <td>
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Traditional Motion with Dwell Segments</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Motions with a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dwell</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> between a Rise or Return Segment are frequently used with in industrial cams. Acronyms for the common motions are:</text></para>
          <list id="1" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">DRD</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> - a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dwell</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> , then a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Rise</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> (or </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Return</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">), then a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dwell</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> (an indexing motion)</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">DRRD</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> - a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dwell</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> then a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Rise</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, then a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Return</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, then a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dwell</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">RRRR</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;" translate="true"> - a continuous sequence of </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Rise</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Returns</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;" translate="true">, no </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dwells.</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Note</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> : a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Rise and Return</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> motion is often a quick turnaround. See </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
